Description:
NO CURVE BALL HERE
"Straight up, Curved Trunk Road is where it's at."
At the forefront of the newly-established Lavender Estate is a stunning four bedroom property. Needless to say you're dotted among some of Officer's best homes and situated among the ever-expanding township of Officer.
Very close to public transport plus walking distance to Maranatha Secondary, Officer Secondary and Bridgewood Primary School. You're also a two minute drive from the new proposed shopping centre.
The house itself is dynamic, featuring:
- Four bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Separate living area;
- Open plan living/dining area;
- Upgraded kitchen with stone bench tops;
- Alfresco;
- Maintainable backyard with a block of 371sqm.
This property is just gone one year old so perfect for investors of first home buyers.

The hunt is over
Perfectly nestled in the highly sought-after Arena Estate is this stunning ex-display home featuring 5 generous bedrooms plus study and four spacious living zones, including theatre room, formal lounge and kid's retreat. This home is impressive in size and ready for the largest of families to enjoy and entertain.
From the moment you enter you will be instantly impressed by the premium finishes and many features on offer, including:
- Spacious Master suite with park views from the balcony, large WIR & a double vanity ensuite with porcelain floor tiles & luxury shower; Four remaining bedrooms all with BIR;
- Downstairs study that is large enough to convert into a guest room for visiting friends and family;
- Separate ground floor powder room;
- Fully appointed kitchen with waterfall Caesar-stone benches plus 900mm stainless steel oven and gas stove-top;
- Theatre room complete with projector, built-in wall speakers and large cinematic screen;
- Two outdoor entertaining zones, including alfresco and oversized spa, surrounded by beautifully landscaped and maintenance-free gardens;
- Large backyard with garden shed and ample room for the kids to play;
- Evaporative cooling, ducted heating, solar panels, ducted vacuum, alarm system and internal Bluetooth speakers throughout.
With so many upgrades and close proximity to schools, shops and sporting fields, this magnificent home is sure to impress.

NOTHING SMALL ABOUT BIGGS
"One of the most affordable properties left in the Officer market."
First-home buyers take note. Investors start sharpening your pencil. This house is for you.
Dotted among some of Arcadia's finest properties, 11 Biggs Street is within walking distance to Bridgewood Primary School and Officer Secondary School and literally only a few doors down from parkland and playgrounds.
The property is complimented by local shopping centres and is a two minute drive from the proposed retail shopping centre. You're also walking distance to the Officer train station.
Now that you're sold on the area, let's talk about the house that's only one year old. Featuring:
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living dining room;
- Stainless steel appliances with 900mm oven and cooktop;
- Walk-in pantry and stone bench tops;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage with internal access;
- Landscaped yards, front and back;
- Recycled water supply and NBN ready.
The owners are flexible on settlement and are waiting for your next move.
